* {{ill|Earth God Shrine|ja|地神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth God Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}

== Access ==
* Approximately a 25-minute walk from [[:en:Shimoura Station|Shimoura Station]] on the [[:en:Tokushima Line|Tokushima Line]] (JR Shikoku).
* Approximately a 20-minute walk from [[:en:Ushinoshima Station|Ushijima Station]] on the same line.

